ropical weeds Sorghum halapense (1%) and Rottboellia cochinchinensis (0.2%). Grasses invade this forest where disturbance coincides with seed dispersal by motor vehicles, while dispersal limitation apparently prevents invasion of many sites otherwise suitable for grass recruitment (i.e., felling and natural gaps).", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Veldman, Joseph W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Putz, Francis E.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Chapter 3", "biodiversity", "environment assessment", "IPBES", "Alien Invasive Species Assessment AIS", "invasive species"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/367cb910d73b82171094e9974ae8233e", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/a9bbeb768c42be37dc31d78ed0f2301a182c3e953da2ea34ca4af5a088db2b0f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/2352922/items/MEWWU4ZQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/2352922/items/MEWWU4ZQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/9f3accb7c43b150c5a6e60c51e43108e!/b160887-163037", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/359bd494433933b868f85e88d3437f76", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.1111/j.1744-7429.201 0.00647.x", "relation": "isVariantFormOf", "resource_type": "publication", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.7430682", "relation": "isCitedBy", "resource_type": "publication-report", "scheme": "doi"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "6", "pages": "697-703", "title": "Biotropica", "volume": "42"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/367cb910d73b82171094e9974ae8233e"}, {"ident